    riskFactors: ["Smoking history (COPD, lung cancer)", "Occupational exposures (asbestos, silica, coal dust)", "Immunosuppression (opportunistic pneumonias)", "Prolonged immobility (PE, atelectasis)", "Recent surgery (especially abdominal/thoracic)", "Aspiration risk (altered consciousness, dysphagia)", "Mechanical ventilation (VAP, barotrauma)", "Sepsis and systemic inflammation (ARDS)", "Obesity (restrictive lung mechanics)", "Cystic fibrosis and bronchiectasis"],
